  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When this card would be played from the hand, if there're
    6 or fewer total cards in both players' security stacks, reduce the play cost
    by 5.[On Play] [When Digivolving] Suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon.[All Turns]
    [Once Per Turn] When a Digimon becomes suspended, you may have 1 of your opponent's
    Digimon get -4000 DP and gain \uFF1CSecurity Attack -1\uFF1E (This Digimon checks
    1 fewer security card) until the end of their turn."
